      "span_text": "Membranes were probed with the 104L, 104F and 104S probes [CITATION_1] at 42°C for 1.5 hours and then washed twice with 2 × SSC 0.1% SDS for 5 min at room temperature, followed by two washings with 0.2 × SSC 0.1% SDS at 42°C for the three kdr alleles (15 minutes per wash).",
